{"type": "article", "id": 9556, "title": "MCM & Beats by Dre 联名系列单品", "description": "", "date": "2015-05-14T07:14:29Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 11, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605235501AKbTCkXQyGl04N3g.png", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;\">\r\n\t</p>\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t\tMCM 和 Beats by Dre 最近合作推出了一个联名系列，其中包括 Beats Studio 头戴式耳机，Beats Tour 入耳式耳机和 Beats Pill 蓝牙音箱三种单品，每件单品都配备有一个 MCM 保护套。配色上采用的是 MCM 经典的黑色与金色搭配。这个系列现在预计今年6 月份发售，MCM 的粉丝们可以<a href=\"http://cn.beatsbydre.com/headphone/beats-mcm-collection.html?icid=internal_Home%20Page_na_MCM_KR_na_MCMNotifyMeSlider\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>关注详细信息。\r\n\t</p>\r\n\t<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052354580eF7yus6hfr3XNEm.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.60092593\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235458PL603Kkn4gwReJ1V.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.63888889\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235459xogLqKP54XmEcabM.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.67407407\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052354593ALVnwGhv56byJsj.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.65925926\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235500QeAqDphVmuTvRSJd.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.7212963\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235500HoibavMy07QZFfV8.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.6787037\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n\t</p>\r\n\n\n"}